Deep Dive Authentication

how cookies work to for the api to communicate with the browser
    - cookies comes from "magic cookies"
        - text packages (little data packets) that the browser can read
        - sites can't read other sites cookies
    - placed inside your browser session (even after you restart, etc.)
    - "with credentials: True" allows the cookies to be created

using Postman
    - Postman is an api testing tool